public static final class Contacts.ContactMethods
extends Object
implements BaseColumns, Contacts.ContactMethodsColumns, Contacts.PeopleColumns

This table stores all non-phone contact methods and a reference to the person that the contact method belongs to.

lookupProviderNameFromId

public static String lookupProviderNameFromId(int protocol)
This looks up the provider name defined in android.provider.Im.ProviderNames from the predefined IM protocol id. This is used for interacting with the IM application.

参数：
protocol - the protocol ID
返回：
the provider name the IM app uses for the given protocol, or null if no provider is defined for the given protocol

longitude - the longitude for the address
